NAME
	hash_sha1 - SHA-1 message digest

SYNOPSIS
	string hash_sha1(string str, string extra...)


DESCRIPTION
	Compute the 160 bit SHA-1 message digest of the concatenation of all
	string arguments.  The result is a string of 20 characters.

SEE ALSO
	kfun/hash_crc16, kfun/hash_crc32, kfun/hash_md5
